OL,3,CBMW hails 'global success' of the Mini
OL,4,Cas modern version hits 25 years
OL,6,FCar-maker BMW Group has hailed the
OL,7,F"global success" of the Mini as it
OL,8,Fmarked the 25th anniversary of the
OL,9,Fmodern version.
OL,11,FThe first new generation Mini rolled
OL,12,Foff the production line at the
OL,13,Fcompany's factory in Oxford on April
OL,14,F26 2001.
OL,16,FThis was "the start of a new chapter"
OL,17,Ffor a car that was already "firmly
OL,18,Festablished as a cultural icon", BMW
OL,19,FGroup said.
