OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776949868
OL,3,CBMW hails 'global success' of the Mini
OL,4,Cas modern version hits 25 years
OL,6,FNearly 4.7 million Minis have been
OL,7,Fbuilt in Oxford over the past quarter
OL,8,Fof a century.
OL,10,FThey have been exported to more than
OL,11,F100 countries.
OL,13,FMini body parts have been made at
OL,14,FBMW's Swindon factory since early 2001.
OL,16,FMore than 3,000 people are employed
OL,17,Facross the Oxford and Swindon plants.
