PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776949868
OL,3,CBMW hails 'global success' of the Mini
OL,4,Cas modern version hits 25 years
OL,6,FMarkus Gruneisl, BMW Group's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive for UK manufacturing, said:
OL,8,F"This 25-year milestone is a proud
OL,9,Fmoment for Mini and for everyone
OL,10,Finvolved in its production here in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,F"From the very beginning, our plants
OL,14,Fin Oxford and Swindon have been at the
OL,15,Fheart of Mini's global success,
OL,16,Fcombining exceptional craftsmanship
OL,17,Fwith innovation.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
