PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776949868
OL,3,CBMW hails 'global success' of the Mini
OL,4,Cas modern version hits 25 years
OL,6,F"Above all, it is our people - their
OL,7,Fcreativity, expertise and pride in
OL,8,Fwhat they do - that continue to make
OL,9,FMini so special."
OL,11,FThe first Mini was launched in 1959 to
OL,12,Fmeet demand for affordable motoring.
OL,14,FThe small cars - easy to manoeuvre and
OL,15,Fwith an unusual shape, soon became
OL,16,Fpopular, featuring as getaway cars in
OL,17,Fmovie The Italian Job and being driven
OL,18,Fby pop stars and fashion legends.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
